,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"不過，明明我在有記憶之前，就已經開始打鼓了，\n但我現在還是打得不好","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event142-05-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"才沒有這回事喔！？　我覺得益木學姊不論面對怎樣的曲子\n都能把它演奏成自己的風格這點真的非常厲害，還有還有，\n益木學姊的鼓聲給人一種滿懷期待的感覺……！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event142-05-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"先，先冷靜一下！\n我的意思是，現在這種情況讓我不太滿意","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event142-05-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"原，原來是這樣……抱歉，我太驚訝了所以……\n不過啊，在有記憶之前就開始打鼓這點真的很厲害呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"eve